Nandito si Elder Marquis Murong.

243
00:15:33,870 --> 00:15:35,470
Naghihintay ang kanyang Grace sa loob.

244
00:15:57,440 --> 00:15:58,700
Elder Marquis Murong,

245
00:15:58,960 --> 00:15:59,910
Humihingi ako ng paumanhin sa pagdukot

246
00:15:59,910 --> 00:16:00,910
Your Grace kanina.

247
00:16:00,910 --> 00:16:02,440
Iyon ay ganap na aking ginawa.

248
00:16:02,670 --> 00:16:03,870
Kung may dapat kang sisihin,

249
